WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.335 --> 00:00:02.302
[bell rings]

00:00:02.336 --> 00:00:04.071
- ALL RIGHT, LISTEN UP, Y'ALL.

00:00:04.104 --> 00:00:07.040
I'M Y'ALL'S SUBSTITUTE TEACHER,
MR. GARVEY.

00:00:07.074 --> 00:00:10.677
I TAUGHT SCHOOL FOR 20 YEARS
IN THE INNER CITY,

00:00:10.711 --> 00:00:13.113
SO DON'T EVEN THINK
ABOUT MESSING WITH ME.

00:00:13.146 --> 00:00:15.415
Y'ALL FEEL ME?
- MM-HMM.

00:00:15.449 --> 00:00:18.952
- OKAY.
LET'S TAKE ROLL HERE.

00:00:18.986 --> 00:00:22.890
JAY QUELLIN.

00:00:22.923 --> 00:00:24.458
WHERE'S JAY QUELLIN AT?

00:00:24.491 --> 00:00:27.828
NO JAY QUELLIN HERE?

00:00:27.861 --> 00:00:29.296
- [clears throat]
- YEAH.

00:00:29.329 --> 00:00:31.932
- UH, DO YOU MEAN JACQUELINE?

00:00:31.965 --> 00:00:34.968
- OKAY. SO THAT'S
HOW IT'S GONNA BE.

00:00:35.002 --> 00:00:36.370
Y'ALL WANNA PLAY.

00:00:36.403 --> 00:00:38.505
OKAY, THEN.

00:00:38.539 --> 00:00:41.208
I GOT MY EYE ON YOU,
JAY QUELLIN.

00:00:44.478 --> 00:00:46.713
BALAKAY.

00:00:46.747 --> 00:00:49.750
WHERE IS BALAKAY AT?

00:00:49.783 --> 00:00:53.687
THERE'S NO BALAKAY HERE TODAY?

00:00:53.720 --> 00:00:54.688
YES, SIR.

00:00:54.721 --> 00:00:58.058
- MY NAME IS BLAKE.
- BL...

00:00:58.091 --> 00:01:00.494
ARE YOU OUT
OF YOUR GODDAMN MIND?

00:01:00.527 --> 00:01:03.163
[mocking voice] BLAKE.
WHAT?

00:01:03.197 --> 00:01:05.065
DO YOU WANNA GO TO WAR, BALAKEY?
- NO.

00:01:05.098 --> 00:01:06.800
- 'CAUSE WE COULD GO TO WAR.
- NO.

00:01:06.834 --> 00:01:10.404
- I'M FOR REAL.
I'M FOR REAL.

00:01:10.437 --> 00:01:14.675
SO YOU BETTER CHECK YOURSELF.

00:01:14.708 --> 00:01:17.544
DEE-NICE.

00:01:17.578 --> 00:01:21.381
IS THERE A DEE-NICE?

00:01:21.415 --> 00:01:25.752
IF ONE OF Y'ALL SAYS
SOME SILLY-ASS NAME...

00:01:25.786 --> 00:01:29.723
THIS WHOLE CLASS
IS GONNA FEEL MY WRATH.

00:01:29.756 --> 00:01:32.526
NOW, DEE-NICE.
- DO YOU MEAN DENISE?

00:01:32.559 --> 00:01:35.863
- SON OF A BITCH!

00:01:35.896 --> 00:01:37.865
YOU SAY YOUR NAME RIGHT,
RIGHT NOW.

00:01:37.898 --> 00:01:38.999
- DENISE?
- YOU SAY IT RIGHT.

00:01:39.099 --> 00:01:40.100
- DENISE.
- CORRECTLY.

00:01:40.100 --> 00:01:41.101
- DENISE.
- RIGHT.

00:01:41.101 --> 00:01:42.102
- DENISE.
- RIGHT.

00:01:42.135 --> 00:01:43.337
- DEE-NICE.
- THAT'S BETTER.

00:01:43.370 --> 00:01:44.471
- [sighs]
- THANK YOU.

00:01:44.505 --> 00:01:48.108
NOW, AY-AY-RON.

00:01:48.108 --> 00:01:49.910
WHERE ARE YOU?

00:01:49.943 --> 00:01:53.180
WHERE IS AY-AY-RON RIGHT NOW?

00:01:53.213 --> 00:01:55.115
NO AY-AY RON, HUH?

00:01:55.115 --> 00:01:59.953
WELL, YOU BETTER BE SICK,
DEAD, OR MUTE, AY-AY-RON!

00:02:00.053 --> 00:02:03.557
- HERE.
OH, MAN.

00:02:03.590 --> 00:02:05.392
- WHY DIDN'T YOU ANSWER ME
THE FIRST TIME I SAID IT, HUH?

00:02:05.425 --> 00:02:06.860
- HUH?
- YOU KNOW, I'M JUST ASKING YOU.

00:02:06.894 --> 00:02:08.495
I SAID IT,
LIKE, FOUR TIMES.

00:02:08.529 --> 00:02:12.366
SO WHY DIDN'T YOU SAY IT THE
FIRST TIME I SAID, "AY-AY-RON?"

00:02:15.068 --> 00:02:16.570
- BECAUSE IT'S PRONOUNCED
"AARON."

00:02:16.603 --> 00:02:20.474
- SON OF A BITCH!
[clattering]

00:02:20.507 --> 00:02:23.443
YOU DONE MESSED UP, AY-AY RON,
NOW TAKE YOUR ASS ON DOWN

00:02:23.477 --> 00:02:25.612
TO OH-SHAG-HENNESY'S OFFICE
RIGHT NOW AND TELL HIM

00:02:25.646 --> 00:02:28.382
EXACTLY WHAT YOU DID!

00:02:28.415 --> 00:02:32.219
- WHO?
- OH-SHAG-HENNESY!

00:02:32.252 --> 00:02:33.353
- PRINCIPAL O'SHAUGHNESSY?

00:02:33.387 --> 00:02:35.956
- GET OUT OF MY GODDAMN
CLASSROOM BEFORE I BREAK

00:02:35.989 --> 00:02:37.524
MY FOOT OFF
IN YOUR ASS!

00:02:37.558 --> 00:02:39.860
INSUBORDINATE...

00:02:39.893 --> 00:02:42.930
AND CHURLISH.

00:02:46.500 --> 00:02:48.402
TYM-OH-THEE.

00:02:48.435 --> 00:02:50.370
- PRESENT.
- THANK YOU!

